query:
SELECT ps.id, ps.colaborador, ps.cargo, ps.departamento
FROM planes_sustitucion ps
WHERE ps.puestoClave = 'Si' AND ps.id NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT planSustitucionId FROM planes_sucesion)
LIMIT 1;
